
---

## 📁 `.gitattributes`

Same as before — suitable for C# projects:

```gitattributes
# Treat all C# files as text
*.cs text

# Normalize line endings for consistency
*.cs text eol=lf
*.csproj text eol=lf
*.sln text eol=lf

# Mark build output as binary
bin/** binary
obj/** binary

# Default for all files
* text=auto

# Handle Markdown files
*.md text
